name: labor_parameter_q
action: <*ASSIGNVALUE(labor_parameter_q:[IF](<*ISSELECTED(Quality of Customer Input.Static Provided by Customer)*>){0.5}{[IF](<*ISSELECTED(Quality of Customer Input.Old Graphic)*>){0.9}{[IF](<*ISSELECTED(Quality of Customer Input.Sketch)*>){1}{[IF](<*ISSELECTED(Quality of Customer Input.Clouded P&ID)*>){2}{[IF](<*ISSELECTED(Quality of Customer Input.Unclouded P&ID)*>){2.5}{0}[ENDIF]}[ENDIF]}[ENDIF]}[ENDIF]}[ENDIF])*>
description:
If qci = Static Provided by Customer, Q = 0.5,
Else If qci = Old Graphic, Q = 0.9
Else If qci = Sketch, Q = 1,
Else If qci = Clouded P&ID, Q = 2
Else If qci = Unclouded P&ID, Q = 2.5
